quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  104,4,"Ngwamba! Chisimu chene takaponyedwe ku Hutwama."
  104,5,"Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Hutwama?"
  104,6,"Wele ni Moto wa Allah wachikolelele (wakuteketulanya chilichose chakuponyedwamo)."
  105,1,"Ana nganinyyiona yaŵatite Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) pakwajonanga achinsyene ndembo (ŵaŵayikaga kugumula Likaaba)?"
  105,2,"Ana nganagatenda malindi gao kuŵa gakusokonechela?"
  105,3,"Ni ŵatumichisye ŵanganyao ijuni mikutula-mikutula."